data.text:
Leland was born January 24, 1967 in Wheeling, WV to the late Melvin & Barbara Bonovich Dickinson.

He was a member of the Wellsburg Moose Lodge.

Leland is preceded in death by his parents, Melvin Dickinson & Barbara Bonovich Dickinson.

He is survived by his wife of 30 years, Tracey Humes Dickinson; his children, Jacob (Nicole) Dickinson, John (Wendy) Dickinson, and Kaytlyn (Brandon) Dickinson; his grandsons, Luka Dickinson & Austin Shaw; his sister, Judy Dickinson; and several fur babies.

Honoring Leland’s wishes, there will be no visitation.

A celebration of life will be held at a later date at the convenience of the family. Arrangements by Kepner Funeral Home 2101 Warwood Ave. Wheeling (304- 277-2722).

Memorial contributions may be made to Brooke County Animal Shelter at 797 Mac Barnes Dr. Beech Bottom, WV 26030 (304-394-0800).
